Package se.dao

se.dao contains Data Access Objects classes which is ued to perform CRUD operations with the database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    agdDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for retrieval for Automatic Group Detection function
    CombinationGenerator
    Combination Generator used to permutate combinations for AGD
    demographicDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for retrieval for breakdown by year and gender
    HeatmapDAO
    Database Access Object to access database to retrieve data for heatmap
    LocationDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for CRUD operations regarding location
    LocationLookupDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for CRUD operations regarding location Lookup
    SubsetIterator<E>
    For faster iteration through the different list types.
    topKDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for retrieval of data for Top K functions
    UserDAO
    Database Access Object to access database for CRUD operations regarding users
